[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レースナちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00064",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "イザナちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00065",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "……いよいよだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00066",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00067",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "フリーゲンを出発した時は、\nこんな旅になるだなんて思ってもなかったなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00068",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "騎士試験を受けて、騎士になって……\nそれからのことなんて、ぜんぜん考えてなかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00069",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "私も。果ての大陸を見つける旅……きっと、\n途方もなく大変なものになるとは思ってたけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00070",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "頂獣と戦ったり、極夜の錬金党や九偉人たちと\n対立したり……そんなの、ぜんぜん考えてなかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00071",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……果ての大陸を見つけて、錬金術を復興して、\n立派な錬金術士になる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00072",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それが、こんなにも覚悟がいることだったなんて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00073",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "……怖い？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00074",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……怖いよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00075",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "でもね。色んなことを目の当たりにして、そのたびに\n考えて、考えて……おかげではっきりと見えてきたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00076",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "私が、やるべきこと。\nやらなくちゃいけないこと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00077",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "果ての大陸にたどり着けば、大量のマナが手に入って、\nそうすれば錬金術は復興して、みんなが幸せになれる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00078",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それを信じて疑わなかったけど……\nきっとそれだけじゃダメなんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00079",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "果ての大陸はないかもしれない。\nあったとしても、マナはないのかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00080",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "マナがあったとしても、錬金術は使われ方次第で\nいいものにも悪いものにもなる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00081",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もしかしたら、錬金術が復興したことで、\n何か悪いことが起こるかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00082",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "私がやらなきゃいけないのは、\nその「かもしれない」の先を考えておくことなんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00083",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "イザナちゃん。改めて、約束する。\n私、立派な錬金術士になる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00084",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "錬金術をちゃんと復興して……正しく復興して……\nみんなを幸せにできるように",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00085",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "きっとそれが、錬金術士の第一人者として、\n責任を持つっていうことなんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00086",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "……うん。それでこそレスナちゃんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00087",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "そしてアタシは、最強の騎士になって、\nずっとレスナちゃんをそばで守り続ける！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00088",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "このハンマーは、レスナちゃんを守るために\nあるんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00089",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふ、ありがとね。\nそれでこそイザナちゃんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00090",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "約束",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00091",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、約束",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00092",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]